<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-15265] Index summary redistribution can start even when compactions are paused</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15265</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we pause autocompaction for upgradesstables/scrub/cleanup etc we pause all compaction strategies to make sure we can grab all sstables, index summary redistribution does not pause and this can cause us to fail the operation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13249286">CASSANDRA-15265</key>
            <summary>Index summary redistribution can start even when compactions are paused</summary>
